    <div style="display: grid; justify-content: center;">
        <img src="/images/model.png" style="width: 548px;" />
    </div>
    <p>Deep Physics is a compact <a href="">DNN</a> model trained to simulate physics. It uses a snapshot in time to predict the next state(s) of a physical system.</p>
    <br/><br/>
    <h2>Why Deep Phyiscs?</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; justify-content: center;">
        <img src="/images/intuitive_physics.png" style="width: 548px" />
    </div>
    <p>Deep Physics is not trying to compete with state of the art physics engines. This research explores the concept of <a href="">Intuitive Physics</a>, a possible subset of General AI.</p>
    <br/><br/>
